thread.title_full: Fast Cover Travel Insurance reviewed by Diane

author: Diane
title: Diane
text:
I like fast cover ,,use it for all my travel plans..the site is colourful and above all so easy to navigate
I would never consider any other insurance plan
it is very reasonably priced ,and offers many benefits
I took my grand daughter to hong kong and she was free on this insurance plan with fast cover,,,cant get better than that,,a real saving
